    <documentation type="rights">These files have been created from data files available at the NASA ESPO data archive. For each flight, the individual
      measurement files have been averaged at 1 minute, merged into single files, and saved in NetCDF format by NCAR/ACD (F.Wu and L.Emmons). Please consult the
      original files for additional information regarding the measurement techniques and comments on interpreting the data. Users of these data files are
      expected to follow the NASA ESPO Archive guidelines for use of the SOLVE data, including consulting with the PIs of the individual measurements for
      interpretation and credit.
    </documentation>

